name: LunchPicker
0:
”Alexa, ask Lunch Picker where should I go for lunch?”
”Alexa, ask Lunch Picker where should we go for lunch?”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lunch picker
des:
Random picker for lunch suggestions. Ask your alexa device "Alexa, ask Lunch Picker where should I go for lunch?". The list is hard-coded, but perhaps will be updated for adding your own through voice commands. 

Ask Lunch Picker to exit/stop/cancel to exit the app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
